> Top News Rep. Ellmers addresses House GOP on email rumors FILE - In this Oct. 4, 2011 Rep. Renee Ellmers, R-N.C . speaks on Capitol Hill in Washington. Ellmers thanked fellow Republicans for their support Friday after many received incendiary emails alleging an affair between her and House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy, according to two Republicans in the closed-door meeting. (AP Photo/Harry Hamburg, File) 
